  "_note": "LIVE APPLY - formula-backed pre-clamp plan table demo for immediate/basic actions. Intended tests: single-hit basic attacks and Ninja dual wield. Data mod should stay disabled. The runtime chooses the source via current ba=1 immediate action state, prequeues eager positive-debit plans for nearby possible targets, uses the pre-clamp unit pointer as the authoritative target, and applies max(1, attacker.pa * 10 - target.faith) before vanilla HP apply. Basic attacks may have action id 0, so this profile explicitly allows zero-action-id active sources. Immediate plans allow two writes and do not require expected HP so dual wield can rewrite both hits.",
